metadata.name: GOODNIGHT.exe
metadata.description:
Under the 🌙's soft, twinkling light,
A fluffy 🐰 hops, so light.

Her ears perk up, so sweet and neat,
Her eyes shine bright, with wonder deep. 👀🐰💫

The grass, a carpet of dew-kissed green,
Like a soft and cozy fairy scene. 🌱💧

🌟✨🌈 Art by 8BitFantasy <3
